## Summary

There was an issue with the version of `/google-vertexai` that was in use (0.2.13) causing errors to be converted to `Cannot read properties of undefined (reading 'Symbol(Symbol.asyncIterator)')` due to an issue with an older version of gaxios - the latest version of the library has
```yaml
{
  "errorMessage": "Cannot read properties of undefined (reading 'Symbol(Symbol.asyncIterator)')",
  "errorDetails": {},
  "n8nDetails": {
    "time": "8/17/2025, 12:46:30 PM",
    "n8nVersion": "1.107.2 (Self Hosted)",
    "binaryDataMode": "default"
  }
}
```

